#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr "運作方式"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "Understanding the push notification flow"
msgstr "了解推播通知流程"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "1. User Subscription"
msgstr "1. 使用者訂閱"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid ""
"When a user visits your site, their browser requests permission to show "
"notifications. If granted, the browser creates a unique push subscription "
"and sends it to your server."
msgstr ""
"使用者造訪你的網站時，其瀏覽器會請求顯示通知的權限。若獲得授權，瀏覽器會建立"
"唯一的推播訂閱並傳送至你的伺服器。"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "2. Event Triggers"
msgstr "2. 事件觸發"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid ""
"When something happens (new comment, post, message, etc.), the plugin "
"detects the event through Fluent Community, Better Messages, or Fluent "
"Messaging hooks."
msgstr ""
"當事件發生時（新留言、文章、訊息等），外掛透過 Fluent Community、Better "
"Messages 或 Fluent Messaging 的 hooks 偵測事件。"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "3. Notification Delivery"
msgstr "3. 通知傳送"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid ""
"The server sends the notification to the push service (FCM for Android, APNs "
"for iOS, etc.), which delivers it to the user's device."
msgstr ""
"伺服器將通知傳送至推播服務（Android 為 FCM，iOS 為 APNs 等），再由推播服務傳"
"送至使用者裝置。"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "4. User Interaction"
msgstr "4. 使用者互動"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid ""
"When the user clicks the notification, they are taken directly to the "
"relevant page (post, comment, message, etc.)."
msgstr "使用者點選通知時，會直接跳轉至相關頁面（文章、留言、訊息等）。"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "疑難排解"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "Common issues and how to fix them"
msgstr "常見問題及解決方式"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "Notifications not being received"
msgstr "沒有收到通知"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
