#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "Browser supports push notifications"
msgstr "瀏覽器支援推播通知"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "User is subscribed (check Subscribers tab)"
msgstr "使用者已訂閱（請檢查訂閱者分頁）"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "Permission request not showing"
msgstr "未顯示權限請求"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid ""
"The browser may have blocked permission requests. Users need to manually "
"enable notifications in their browser settings, then refresh the page."
msgstr ""
"瀏覽器可能已封鎖權限請求。使用者需要在瀏覽器設定中手動啟用通知，然後重新整理"
"頁面。"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "Notifications work on desktop but not mobile"
msgstr "通知在桌面版正常但行動裝置無效"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "Mobile push notifications require:"
msgstr "行動裝置推播通知需要："

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "HTTPS (mandatory for mobile)"
msgstr "HTTPS（行動裝置必須）"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "iOS 16.4 or later for Safari"
msgstr "Safari 需 iOS 16.4 或更新版本"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "Chrome, Firefox, or Edge on Android"
msgstr "Android 上的 Chrome、Firefox 或 Edge"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "User to add site to home screen (iOS)"
msgstr "使用者需將網站加到主畫面（iOS）"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "Error: \"Subscription expired\""
msgstr "錯誤：「訂閱已過期」"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid ""
"Push subscriptions can expire. The plugin automatically removes expired "
"subscriptions. Users will need to refresh the page to re-subscribe."
msgstr ""
"推播訂閱可能會過期，外掛會自動移除過期訂閱，使用者需重新整理頁面以重新訂閱。"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid "VAPID key mismatch error"
msgstr "VAPID 金鑰不符錯誤"

#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid ""
"If you regenerate VAPID keys, all existing subscriptions become invalid. Use "
"the \"Cleanup Invalid\" button in the Subscribers tab to remove them."
msgstr ""
"若你重新產生 VAPID 金鑰，所有現有訂閱都將失效。請使用訂閱者分頁中的「清理無效"
"訂閱」按鈕來移除它們。"

