#: views/tabs/tab-help.php
msgid ""
"iOS Safari requires users to add your site to their home screen before push "
"notifications will work. This creates a PWA (Progressive Web App) that can "
"receive notifications."
msgstr ""
"iOS Safari 要求使用者將你的網站加到主畫面後，推播通知才能運作。這會建立一個可"
"以接收通知的 PWA（漸進式網頁應用程式）。"

